        ],
        "text": "General specifications  \nProduct name  \nSOLE RA LED  \nApplication area  \nIdeal for offices, commercial spaces, hallways, corridors, \nclassrooms, waiting areas, or homes in areas with low \nhumidity. \nAdvantages  \n− High -quality light for a comfortable ambiance  \n− High protection rating  \n− Low energy consumption  \n− Low maintenance costs  \n− Easy installation  \nLight source  \nLED  \nColor temperature  \n4000 /4500  \nColor rendering index (CRI)  \n≥80  \nType of light distribution  \nSymmetrical \nDegree of protection against dust/water ingress\n \nIP40 \nDegree of protection against mechanical impacts\n \nIK02 \nOperating temperature range  \n-20C....+45C \nWarranty \n5 years  \nElectrical characteristics\n \n",
        "type": 0
